node.text: i won’t forget you that’s for sure. you were the hardest year of my life. i did a lot of embarrassing and stupid shit this year but i also have never laughed and smiled more. i learned SO much this year. overall i cannot believe God blessed me with such a crazy wonderful life cause guess what IT’S A WONDERFUL LIFE AND… i made it through the year. here’s to A NEW DECADE. lets make it count biotches 🥳

node.text: i cannot believe i get to call this beautiful goddess my SISTER. my YOUNGER sister. THIS BETCH IS 17 TODAY. you’ve been my better half ever since you popped your little head into this world. i cannot say enough good things about you, quite frankly i don’t know what i would do without you or who i would be without you. i look up to YOU! like i actually look up to you... silly model girl. bruh go dance into year 17 you perfect human i gotta go wipe my tears 😭 stop growing up. i love you more than you could ever know el, happy birthday❤️
